    <briefdescription>
<para>Provides an <computeroutput>execute</computeroutput> implementation that maps XACC IR to a suitable JSON message for execution on QB hardware. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Execution is in two phases:<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Circuit submission via HTTP POST to QB hardware device</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Using the returned ID, form a HTTP GET request and poll repeatedly until results are returned </para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
